https://twitter.com/WorkWombatman/status/1686114452708724736?s=20"><ins>产品负责人布拉德·罗塞蒂 (Brad Rossetti) 表示，该计划已经上线，</ins></a>因此，如果您有任何损坏的 Xbox 控制器，现在是时候考虑修复它们了。微软似乎还允许其他零售商销售这些替换零件，例如<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.ifixit.com/Parts/Microsoft_Game_Console_Accessory"><ins>自助维修大师 iFixit。</ins></a></p><p>微软并不是最近唯一一家允许 DIY 修复的游戏巨头。索尼的<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/playstation-dualsense-edge-review-sonys-pricey-but-powerful-sidekick-for-the-ps5-130041956.html"><ins>DualSense Edge 控制器</ins></a>实际上附带了替换控制杆模块，尽管该公司不通过在线商店销售其他部件。任天堂不出售其控制器的维修组件，但当出现可怕的 Joy-Con 漂移情况时，它将<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/nintendo-offers-unlimited-free-repairs-for-joy-con-drift-issue-in-europe-062645235.html"><ins>免费维修 Joy-Con</ins></a> 。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上，网址为 https://www.engadget.com/microsoft-starts-looking-replacement-parts-for-xbox-gamepads-174023573.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/microsoft-starts-selling-replacement-parts-for-xbox-gamepads-174023573.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 9614cf41-5f9a-4fd4-8426-11b623678e2a</guid><dc:creator>劳伦斯·邦克</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Tue, 01 Aug 2023 17:40:23 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1690911625</ingested><modified> 2023-08-01T17:40:30+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Lawrence Bonk]]></category><media:content height="3049" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/4b636b00-308e-11ee-9cbd-df316645a4a9" width="4573"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]><