变为一家拥有实体店、虚拟选项和实验室测试的初级医疗保健提供商。在适当的情况下，您可能只需要与亚马逊企业进行互动。</p><p>这些举措引起了监管机构的审查。尽管联邦贸易委员会在 2 月份表示不会对 One Medical 的收购提出质疑，但它警告称，仍在调查此次合并是否可能因获取健康数据而产生反竞争和隐私问题。欧盟委员会表示，如果发现问题，可能会在稍后对该交易提出质疑。不过，就目前而言，亚马逊的医疗保健雄心并未面临重大阻力——它现在已成为传统诊所的替代方案，至少对于日常问题而言是如此。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/amazons-virtual-healthcare-service-is-now-available-in-every-state-171827351.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/amazons-virtual-healthcare-service-is-now-available-in-every-state-171827351.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> cc34f829-9f25-4299-8bec-6fda52386971</guid><dc:creator>乔恩·芬加斯</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Tue, 01 Aug 2023 17:18:27 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1690909774</ingested><modified> 2023-08-01T17:09:59+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Jon Fingas]]></category><media:content height="1280" medium="image" url="https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/f734e800-3084-11ee-9ff7-c2fcdfb18cc4" width="1920"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="1280" medium="image" url="https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2023-08/f734e800-3084-11ee-9ff7-c2fcdfb18cc4" width="1920"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Amazon]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Amazon Clinic]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Amazon Clinic]]></med